<script src="<%= props.slug %>.js"></script>
<script>
    hljs.registerLanguage('<%= props.slug %>', window.hljsDefine<%= props.pascalCase %>);
    hljs.initHighlightingOnLoad();
</script>
```

Should you use a bundler such as Webpack or Rollup, simply require the core library and the language

